train_dataset = train_dataset.prefetch(buffer_size=AUTOTUNE)
validation_dataset = validation_dataset.prefetch(buffer_size=AUTOTUNE)
test_dataset = test_dataset.prefetch(buffer_size=AUTOTUNE)
In[34]:
data_augmentation = tf.keras.Sequential([
  tf.keras.layers.RandomFlip('horizontal',input_shape=(200,200,3)),
  tf.keras.layers.RandomRotation(0.2),
])

In[40]:
from tensorflow.keras import Sequential
from tensorflow.keras.layers import Rescaling,Conv2D,MaxPooling2D,Flatten,Dense
model = Sequential([
    data_augmentation,
  Rescaling(1./255),
  Conv2D(16, 3, padding='same', activation='relu'), #1000-3+2+1
  MaxPooling2D(),#500
  Conv2D(32, 3, padding='same', activation='relu'),#500-3+3
  MaxPooling2D(),#250
  Conv2D(64, 3, padding='same', activation='relu'),#250
  MaxPooling2D(),#125
    Conv2D(64, 3, padding='same', activation='relu'),#125
  MaxPooling2D(),#62
    Conv2D(64, 3, padding='same', activation='relu'),#62
  MaxPooling2D(),#31
    Conv2D(64, 3, padding='same', activation='relu'),#15
  MaxPooling2D(),#7
  Flatten(),
  Dense(128, activation='relu'),
  Dense(1,activation='sigmoid')
])
